channel.title: Looking for 317 coders
channel.description:
So I am planning to start 317 server. I will check which base I use, maybe 2006 remake or something. This server is not meant to be anything special, just way to learn coding. So if someone wants to start coding with me, adding lots of features and so on add me on skype zeropointxx. Any advanced programmer is also more than welcome :).
P.S. I will quite army in 3 days since then I can start really programming.
